{"id":22,"parent_id":0,"book_id":0,"content_id":1,"language_id":0,"display_order":22,"title":"The New Adventures of Matt and Mandy","subtitle":"","short_title":"The New Adventures of Matt and Mandy","uri":"/friend/2013/09/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"article","uri":"/friend/2013/09/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/friend/2013/09/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.head1"},[".seriesTitle","The New Adventures of Matt & Mandy"]],[".bodyBlock",[".figure",{"id":"f62","uri":"/friend/2013/09/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f62"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/leaders/fr13sep31-matt-and-mandy.jpg"}],[".credit",["p.para",{"id":"p2","uri":"/friend/2013/09/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p2"},"Illustrations by Maryn Roos"]]],[".figure",{"id":"f63","uri":"/friend/2013/09/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f63"},["p.para",{"id":"p3","uri":"/friend/2013/09/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p3"},"Mandy, you haven’t eaten much. Is something wrong?"],["p.para",{"id":"p4","uri":"/friend/2013/09/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p4"},"I was just thinking about these three girls in my class. They’re not very nice. They make fun of me, and I don’t know why."]],[".figure",{"id":"f64","uri":"/friend/2013/09/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f64"},["p.para",{"id":"p5","uri":"/friend/2013/09/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p5"},"Audrey might be OK. I think she just goes along with the other two. I’m trying to be friends with her."],["p.para",{"id":"p6","uri":"/friend/2013/09/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p6"},"Good idea."]],[".figure",{"id":"f65","uri":"/friend/2013/09/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f65"},["p.para",{"id":"p7","uri":"/friend/2013/09/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p7"},"Some of the kids at school make fun of Franco when the teachers aren’t looking."],["p.para",{"id":"p8","uri":"/friend/2013/09/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p8"},"Tuesday when they were teasing him in the hall, I just walked up and started talking to him, and we ignored them."]],[".figure",{"id":"f66","uri":"/friend/2013/09/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f66"},["p.para",{"id":"p9","uri":"/friend/2013/09/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p9"},"Those kids don’t even know Franco. He’s a pretty cool guy."]],[".figure",{"id":"f67","uri":"/friend/2013/09/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f67"},["p.para",{"id":"p10","uri":"/friend/2013/09/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p10"},"Whoa! Now I’m feeling pretty cool myself!"]]]]]],"refs":null}
